{"id":"a8ec160b-160e-41af-97e7-a4a1d3c0a2f9","name":"Dragon Ball Super Action Figure S.H. Figuarts Son Goku Ultra Instinct Toyotarou Edition 14cm","slug":"dragon-ball-super-action-figure-s.h.-fig-1","description":"<p><b>Dragon Ball Super </b>Action Figure of <b>Son Goku Ultra Instinct Toyotarou Edition </b>in <strong>S.H. Figuarts </strong>collection, size approx.14cm. <b>Official product</b> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>SON GOKU</strong> ULTRA INSTINCT -TOYOTAROU Edition- joins <strong>S.H.Figuarts</strong>, totally overseen by TOYOTAROU, illustrator of \"<strong>DRAGON BALL SUPER</strong>\"</p>\n<p>Includes two heads and four expression options for replicating TOYOTAROU's distinctive look, with new coloring designed to evoke the manga appearance of the character! And there's more: the set includes a V Jump Books \"Dragon Ball S.H.Figupedia\" that covers 171 Dragon Ball S.H.Figuarts products. The 144 page book includes an interview with TOYOTAROU and other special features.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><strong>Content :</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Main Body</li>\n<li>Three pairs of optional hands</li>\n<li>Four optional expression parts</li>\n<li>Optional head</li>\n<li>V Jump Books \"Dragon Ball S.H.Figupedia\"</li>\n</ul>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-26T00:14:29.373Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-26T00:14:29.373Z","barcode":"4573102654687","deletedAt":null,"brandId":"3973100e-a304-42f2-b48a-5e810adf1082","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"a8ec160b-160e-41af-97e7-a4a1d3c0a2f9","categoryId":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","category":{"id":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","name":"Collectibles","slug":"collectibles","description":"Auto-imported category: Collectibles","image":null,"parentId":null,"createdAt":"202